<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ecom Password Reset</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-width: 100%;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            background-color: #fafafa;
            color: #222222;
        }

        a {
            color: #000;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.25;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        p {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        table td {
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .email-header {
            background-color: #0070f3;
            padding: 24px;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .email-body {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 24px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .otp-code {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            margin: 24px 0;
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            display: inline-block;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .footer-text {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 24px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>Password Reset Request</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Hello <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>
            <p>
                We received a request to reset the password for your ECom account. Please use the OTP below to verify your identity and proceed with resetting your password:
            </p>
            <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
            <p>
                This OTP is valid for 5 minutes. If you didnâ€™t request a password reset, please ignore this email. Your account will remain secure.
            </p>
            <p>
                If you continue to have trouble, feel free to contact our support team.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-text">
            &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> ECom. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
